&bull; Create, maintain and update trip files for all company travel, including review and preparation for annual audit<br />
&bull; Enter information provided by staff into the database and maintain travel database<br />
&bull; Assist in booking and support in travel for all employees<br />
&bull; Manage company housing in other cities<br />
&bull; Sourcing best travel providers, such as airlines, hotels, conference centers, restaurants for cost efficiency<br />
&bull; Arrange group travel and accommodation for major conferences<br />
&bull; Recommend and stay within approved budget amounts for travel<br />
&bull; Coordinate travel resources for client visits<br />
&bull; Maintaining corporate discount agreements with selected carriers<br />
&bull; Manage company Travel phones</p>
<p>
<strong>QUALIFICATIONS</strong></p>
<p>
